theHarvester - tool designed to gather emails, domain information, hostnames, employee names, subdomains, open ports and banners using search engines and Maltego

Usage:
  theharvester -d <DOMAIN> -b <SOURCES> -s

Options:
  -s         use shodan for searching
  -b         sources list, you can use 'all' for all sources

